  <summary date="2006-11-28T17:35:40Z" status="Introduced in House">Disabled Veterans Adaptive Benefits Improvement Act of 2003 - Increases from: (1) $48,000 to $50,000 the maximum amount authorized to be provided by the Department of Veterans Affairs to certain disabled veterans for the construction of specially adapted housing; (2) $9,250 to $10,000 the maximum amount authorized for specially adapted features within a home; and (3) $9,000 to $11,000 the maximum amount authorized for automobile and adaptive equipment for such veterans.</summary>
